Its been 2 years since I made bhop_edibles_v1 and 2 years later I made v2 and v3 in a span of 2 days

These maps have been a big part of bhop to me since I had so much fun making them.

These have only been on 1 server Ruta's world Bhop (gmod server) and was wanting to release them together when I was finished a few months ago but never had the chance.

So I guess even though I've been done with these maps for a while Ill just give them out now :^]
